It's Staff Fact Friday here at UCP! We are so excited to welcome our new administrative staff for the upcoming school year. Continue reading below for some need to know info about our great leadership!

Up first: Principal Phillip Penn!

Phillip Penn joined ACCEL Schools in 2017 as a school principal with over 12 years of experience as a K-8 educator and administrator. As Executive Principal at ACCEL Schools, he oversees leadership development, instructional programming, operations, and strategic planning for two schools in Cleveland, Ohio. Prior to joining ACCEL Schools, Mr. Penn served in teaching and leadership roles in public and charter schools including ICAN Schools, Clevelandâ€¦
